00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:17,000
have experienced in Human Realm,



00:03:17,260 --> 00:03:19,160
so he made an excuse



00:03:19,940 --> 00:03:21,160
to send Yuan Ji in Human Realm too.



00:03:22,460 --> 00:03:23,360
Now



00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:25,560
