00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:56,980
but at last…



00:03:57,660 --> 00:03:58,600
Maybe



00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:02,760
she has made a choice



00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,440
between Xu Feng and Run Yu.



00:04:05,540 --> 00:04:06,360
