00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:12,580
Yes.



00:14:12,680 --> 00:14:13,540
If you kill her,



00:14:13,880 --> 00:14:15,160
will Xu Feng come back to life?



00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:16,820
When I met her just now,



00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:19,940
I wanted to hack her to death.



00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:21,980
